ive with four semesters worth of ASL instruction? (ASL 1, ASL 2, ASL 3, and ASL 4)  for $79.95?  \nSee \"SuperUSB\" in the ASLUniversity bookstore at: https://lifeprint.com/bookstore/books...\n\nFor free ASL Lessons see:    / billvicars  \nTo learn basic fingerspelling see    • ABC's in ASL: Learn how to Fingerspell!  \n\nAbout your instructor:\nhttp://www.lifeprint.com/asl101/pages...\nWarm regards and love to you all.\nI am grateful for your support.\nDr. Bill\n:)","commandRuns":[{"startIndex":54,"length":25,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBIQ040EGAUiEwiy_piat-uTAxUjFYYAHRwjB71IlJbSuPCdk9EuygEEGwxt_w==","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbS1QSF9vdElyYi1wenp3aVNLaGNPSG90aEQ5d3xBQ3Jtc0tsek5KVHUtb3VzTlNHUzFMNGxObVhWbDNMdlY0M0dMa2RpZ0FSVzBwUXJhLWdtdTZLMmNpT1N6Q2pTMGxsTlRyOFBac1VkdlNRX3cwaHpTYUxNN2hoSnFpOTB2d3ByWlZlWEdvR3FFcUhCTHJYNGVOVQ\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=LqJM7wcUixQ","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_UNKNOWN","rootVe":83769}},"urlEndpoint":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbS1QSF9vdElyYi1wenp3aVNLaGNPSG90aEQ5d3xBQ3Jtc0tsek5KVHUtb3VzTlNHUzFMNGxObVhWbDNMdlY0M0dMa2RpZ0FSVzBwUXJhLWdtdTZLMmNpT1N6Q2pTMGxsTlRyOFBac1VkdlNRX3cwaHpTYUxNN2hoSnFpOTB2d3ByWlZlWEdvR3FFcUhCTHJYNGVOVQ\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=LqJM7wcUixQ","target":"TARGET_NEW_WINDOW","nofollow":true}}}},{"startIndex":166,"length":40,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBIQ040EGAUiEwiy_piat-uTAxUjFYYAHRwjB71IlJbSuPCdk9EuygEEGwxt_w==","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbXFscDBnZ0xEbUxpdXE5Sm01UjJJQzlER2szd3xBQ3Jtc0trY1J2Q0JUeVBOaHlLSUtobXU0SHF6dU8zaGpTdGJFLXAwdkFfSDFDWjhuU001Z3FTMEQ0ZXRadmE4aVVDanJXMEdTNUttczNZY211RnhzSlFaQnlGb2VGUDlleUozeVM0dWlIbjUycXF6UGduU2txRQ\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.payp